  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 1st level, as a bonus action you can generate enough webbing to create Web weapons. </p><p>All Web Weapons have the Multiattack and Lethal 1 weapon properties. When you make a Web Weapon, you create any simple melee weapon or any simple or martial ranged weapon with the Ammunition property, that does not have the Heavy weapon property. </p><p>Weapons with the Ammunition property that you creature do not need to roll ammunition die as you create new ammunition from your webs with each attack.</p>",
